I don't make you happy.

85
00:09:14,287 --> 00:09:16,380
Morning, Sarge.

86
00:09:53,092 --> 00:09:56,619
Hi. Steve Mitchell, Chris Mitchell,
to see Ambassador Gannon, please.

87
00:09:57,663 --> 00:09:59,893
- Welcome to Bucharest, Mr. Mitchell.
- Thank you.

88
00:09:59,932 --> 00:10:02,298
I will let Deputy Tomberlin
know you're here.

89
00:10:02,335 --> 00:10:04,860
- Mr. Mitchell?
- Hi.

90
00:10:04,904 --> 00:10:06,496
