but never mention the angel.

126
00:12:15,401 --> 00:12:18,131
Yeah, right.
I've done four.

127
00:12:18,170 --> 00:12:20,263
- Really?
- Um-hmm.

128
00:12:20,306 --> 00:12:22,365
Prague was the best.

129
00:12:22,675 --> 00:12:25,735
Budapest wasn't bad, either.

130
00:12:25,778 --> 00:12:28,440
