227
00:23:23,702 --> 00:23:27,968
Diplomatic attaché Erica Long.

228
00:23:30,575 --> 00:23:35,410
Your name must have more to do
with your legs, Miss Long...

229
00:23:35,447 --> 00:23:37,642
than your life span.

230
00:23:39,251 --> 00:23:42,152
At least I still have
a life span.

231
00:23:43,822 --> 00:23:47,417
Oh, boy.
We got a live one, here.

232
00:24:06,511 --> 00:24:09,446
Tim...
I'm at the north corridor.

233
00:24:09,481 --> 00:24:11,142
All right.

234
00:24:11,183 --> 00:24:14,050
Stay to the left and the rear
of the building.

235
00:24:14,085 --> 00:24:16,019
Did you get that?
Sir...?

236
00:24:20,192 --> 00:24:22,160
Step out there, and read this.

237
00:24:23,695 --> 00:24:25,060
